			</header>
			{# Description #}
			<p>Aliquam erat volutpat. Nunc egestas purus sit amet nisl tempus fermentum. Sed vitae lectus quam. Pellentesque sit amet tellus risus. Pellentesque et nunc nec turpis hendrerit viverra. Cras dictum lacus in nulla pellentesque porta.</p>
		</article>
		
		{# Promoted post with image #}
		<article class="promoted clearfix">
			<figure class="media">
				<img src="/themes/barca/assets/img/temp/blog-post-image.jpg" alt="" />
			</figure>
			<header> {# Heading #}
				<time datetime="2013-05-26"><b>26</b>05.2013</time> {# Time, promoted items has different date format #}
				<h3><a href="#">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Cras ultricies eros sed augue bibendum rhoncus.</a></h3> {# Title #}
			</header>
			{# Description #}
			<p>Aliquam erat volutpat. Nunc egestas purus sit amet nisl tempus fermentum. Sed vitae lectus quam. Pellentesque sit amet tellus risus. Pellentesque et nunc nec turpis hendrerit viverra. Cras dictum lacus in nulla pellentesque porta.</p>
		</article>
		
		{# Normal post with image #}
		<article class="clearfix">
			{# Heading #}
			<header>
				{# Time #}
				<time datetime="2013-05-26">26/05/2013</time>
				{# Title #}
				<h3><a href="#">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Cras ultricies eros sed augue bibendum rhoncus.</a></h3>
			</header>
			
